    "title": "京东规则动态一览（2025年6月23日-2025年6月27日）",
    "followRuleId": "1254624768095817728",
    "content": "<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则公示】</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\">《<a style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1255789833545191424\">京东开放平台大时尚品类新商激励政策（2025.7.1-2025.9.30）》</a></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2025</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">年Q3入驻的京东开放平台时尚相关类目的商家，当GMV达到相关要求，将可获发专项激励金额，专项激励金用于广告投放。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: #F8F8F9;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: #F8F8F9;\">、【修订】</span><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1255761115896483840\">《京东开放平台商家保证金管理规则》</a></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: #F8F8F9;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">因保证金GMV阈值合并，保证金规则举例部分，按照最新收费挡位同步调整。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1254622809850777600&amp;btype=1\">《京东开放平台非全新商品管理规则》</a></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">新增非全新商品管理要求，包括非全新商品商品信息要求、违规处理措施等。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1255847210776662016\">《京东开放平台店铺综合体验分规则》</a></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">五星店铺认证范围调整为在京东开放平台入驻开店的旗舰店、专卖店、专营店、卖场店店铺。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1255044522015068160&amp;btype=1\">《京东开放平台商品质量不合格细则》</a></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">调整质量违规场景定义②增加综合认定质量问题定义及对应处理措施③删除质量客诉场景④调整附则等相关表述。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">【规则生效】</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-variant-ligatures: normal; text-align: start; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、【修订】<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1253291287357034496\">《京东开放平台不当发布商品或信息细则》</a></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-variant-ligatures: normal; text-align: start; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、修订&rdquo;变更商品&ldquo;场景定义及违规处理措施。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-variant-ligatures: normal; text-align: start; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><strong>关联规则：</strong>&nbsp;<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1253296595865309184&amp;btype=12\">《京东开放平台个人/个体合规管理规则》</a></span></span></span></p>",
